gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 122, Kings 97
gameRecap.excerpt: The Rockets defeated the Kings, 122-97. Jalen Green led all scorers with 23 points for the Rockets, while Alperen Sengun added 17 points, eight rebounds, and a career-high 12 assists in the victory. Kevin Huerter tallied 13 points and three rebounds for the Kings in the losing effort. The Rockets improve to 3-3 on the season, while the Kings fall to 3-3.
